messages.message:
<!here> hello eng! It's been over a month since our last production deployment. It's time for another one. Next week, I plan to do another prod deployment. It also means we need to freeze our codebase and run a UAT.

Let's follow a new deployment timeline.

```
Code freeze by Friday - Feb 22nd.

Complete UAT by Tuesday.

Deploy to Production on Wednesday or Thursday.
```

Any concerns? :slightly_smiling_face:

Similar question: are folks OK with me adding the first chapter or two of “Instabase University” to the official doc site? Working on it today & tomorrow for FRB & GS training. I realize we have great tribal training knowledge, but I’m really antsy to push forward on scalable self-service training materials.
